  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, jump, rewind, and cooperate with your past self in this time-leaping action puzzle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable with a keyboard (※Controller recommended)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move: WASD keys or Arrow keys</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump: J key or Space key</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rewind: Q key or K key</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Menu: Return key<br><br>▼ Aim for the goal by cooperating with your past self</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952990/extras/7b049d93a8fe3fcbcd64109285f2af5c.poster.avif?t=1741313506\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952990/extras/7b049d93a8fe3fcbcd64109285f2af5c.webm?t=1741313506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952990/extras/7b049d93a8fe3fcbcd64109285f2af5c.mp4?t=1741313506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>▼ However, changing past actions causes time paradoxes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952990/extras/5a18bb216349d1ecfbcd40671ff81cb9.poster.avif?t=1741313506\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952990/extras/5a18bb216349d1ecfbcd40671ff81cb9.webm?t=1741313506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952990/extras/5a18bb216349d1ecfbcd40671ff81cb9.mp4?t=1741313506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>▼ Avoiding time paradoxes, breakthrough puzzles with past and future selves</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span clas